OL,6,FWARNING: VIDEO CONTAINS FLASHING IMAGES
OL,8,FA man who crashed a drone at a concert
OL,9,Fon Brighton beach has been convicted
OL,10,Fin the first case of its kind in court.
OL,12,FGiles Dalby lost control of the
OL,13,Faircraft which then crashed into the
OL,14,Fstage during a live music performance.
OL,16,FFootage shows how the aircraft flew
OL,17,Fjust over the heads of people in the
OL,18,Faudience during the event.
