OL,6,FAt Brighton Magistrates' Court this
OL,7,Fmonth, Dalby admitted recklessly or
OL,8,Fnegligently causing or permitting an
OL,9,Faircraft to endanger a person or
OL,10,Fproperty.
OL,12,FHe had used the drone contrary to the
OL,13,FAir Navigation Order during the
OL,14,Fincident on July 24, 2022.
OL,16,FIt is believed to be the first
OL,17,Fprosecution of its kind under the
OL,18,Flegislation.
OL,20,FDalby, 39, was fined #576, with a #230
OL,21,Fsurcharge and #85 costs.
