OL,6,FThe operator is legally responsible
OL,7,Ffor every flight, and must keep the
OL,8,Faircraft in sight at all times.
OL,10,FThe aircraft must be kept below 400ft,
OL,11,Fand must not be flown over a congested
OL,12,Farea.
OL,14,FSussex Police Drone Training Officer
OL,15,FPC Steven Prince said: "Dalby operated
OL,16,Fa drone above a crowded beach concert
OL,17,Fon Brighton beach.
