OL,6,F"He lost control of the aircraft which
OL,7,Fthen crashed into the stage, near to a
OL,8,Fmusician who was in the middle of a
OL,9,Flive performance.
OL,11,F"Dalby is fortunate that no one was
OL,12,Fharmed, but this case should act as a
OL,13,Freminder to all drone operators about
OL,14,Fhow to stay within the law."
OL,16,FJonathan Nicholson, spokesperson at
OL,17,Fthe UK Civil Aviation Authority, said:
OL,18,F"Drones can be great fun to fly and
OL,19,Fare undertaking more and more useful
OL,20,Frules such as delivering medical
